item.title: Aligned Manifestation – Dr. Dolores Fazzino
item.description: The Dr. Dolores Show How often do we become discouraged, particularly when you desire something so badly to manifest, and it hasn't yet? In this thought-provoking episode on The Dr. Dolores Show, we delve deep into the powerful intersection of alignment, manifestation, and integrity, exploring how these concepts intertwine to shape our reality and our creations. Join us as we navigate the transformative journey of creating from a place of love rather than fear and avoidance... Feed: https://www.inspiredchoicesnetwork.com/xml-feed/?id=119054
